title: Local Urban Kitchen
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, American, Juice bar, Delivery, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Offers vegan dishes, including vegan mash sandwich (house-made grain burger), black bean burger, and tofu wrap, and at Thanksgiving a tofurkey special. Also has vegan cheese/cream items to convert other dishes. Gluten-free options. Another location in Point Pleasant Beach.
